OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder,
OL,4,Cafter individual shot with crossbow
OL,6,FA man has been charged with attempted
OL,7,Fmurder after an individual was shot
OL,8,Fwith a crossbow at the University of
OL,9,FSurrey.
OL,11,FPolice were called to reports of a man
OL,12,Fbeing shot with a crossbow at Manor
OL,13,FPark Student Village, Guildford, at
OL,14,Faround 10am on Thursday 4 June.
OL,16,FAlmunthir Daqamah, 21, has been
OL,17,Fcharged with attempted murder,
OL,18,Fpossession of an offensive weapon, two
OL,19,Fcounts of possession of a bladed
OL,20,Farticle and possession of Class B
OL,21,Fdrugs.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
