FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780862761
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder,
OL,4,Cafter individual shot with crossbow
OL,6,FDaqamah is a Saudi national who was a
OL,7,Fformer student at the University of
OL,8,FSurrey.
OL,10,FHe has been in custody since being
OL,11,Farrested by police on Thursday, and
OL,12,Fwill appear at Guildford Magistrates'
OL,13,FCourt this morning.
OL,15,FThe victim of the shooting is a campus
OL,16,Fsecurity officer in his 50s, who was
OL,17,Fairlifted to hospital in London after
OL,18,Fbeing attended to by ambulance crews,
OL,19,Fincluding a critical care paramedic,
OL,20,Fat the scene.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780862761
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder,
OL,4,Cafter individual shot with crossbow
OL,6,FHe was admitted to hospital in a
OL,7,F'serious' condition, but is now in a
OL,8,Fstable condition.
OL,10,FChief Superintendent Jon Groenen said:
OL,11,F"We know how concerning this incident
OL,12,Fis, both for the University community
OL,13,Fand for local residents here in
OL,14,FGuildford, and our officers are
OL,15,Fworking at pace to establish the full
OL,16,Fcircumstances of what occurred.
OL,18,F"There is nothing to suggest this
OL,19,Fincident is terror-related and we are
OL,20,Fnot looking for anyone else in
OL,21,Fconnection with it.
OL,26,@sD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780862761
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder,
OL,4,Cafter individual shot with crossbow
OL,6,F"We continue to work closely with the
OL,7,FUniversity and at this time, I would
OL,8,Fask people to refrain from speculating
OL,9,Fonline to preserve the integrity of
OL,10,Fthe investigation. If you have any
OL,11,Finformation that could assist our
OL,12,Fenquiries, please contact us directly.
OL,14,F"The victim is thankfully now in a
OL,15,Fstable condition. He remains in
OL,16,Fhospital and we continue to provide
OL,17,Fsupport to his family."
OL,19,FSurrey Police are appealing for anyone
OL,20,Fwith information that would assist
OL,21,Ftheir investigation to come forward.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
