PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780862761
OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder,
OL,4,Cafter individual shot with crossbow
OL,6,FA University of Surrey spokesperson
OL,7,Fadded: "We have been informed that our
OL,8,Fcolleague is now in a stable condition
OL,9,Fand our entire community is relieved
OL,10,Fto hear this news. We wish him a full
OL,11,Fand speedy recovery.
OL,13,F"We also want to take this opportunity
OL,14,Fto thank our Campus Safety team. They
OL,15,Fresponded with professionalism and
OL,16,Fcourage to this incident, and their
OL,17,Fcommitment to keeping this community
OL,18,Fsafe is something we are deeply proud
OL,19,Fof.
OL,21,F"Our thoughts are with all of them."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
